Section 1:
1 L.D. 261
2 Date: (Filing No. H- )
3 AGRICULTURE, CONSERVATION AND FORESTRY
5 STATE OF MAINE
6 HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
7 132ND LEGISLATURE
8 FIRST SPECIAL SESSION
9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 164, L.D. 261, “An Act Regarding the
10 Authority of Municipalities to Regulate Timber Harvesting”
11 Amend the bill in section 2 in subsection 8 by striking out all of the 2nd blocked
12 paragraph (page 1, lines 26 and 27 in L.D.).
13 Amend the bill in section 2 in subsection 8 in paragraph E-1 in the last line (page 2,
14 line 44 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "with" the following: 'the process
15 requirements of'
16 Amend the bill in section 2 in subsection 8 by striking out all of paragraph E-2 (page
17 3, lines 1 and 2 in L.D.).
18 Amend the bill in section 3 in subsection 9 in paragraph C in the first line (page 3, line
19 23 in L.D.) by striking out the following: "on" and inserting the following: 'that has been
20 adopted prior to'
21 Amend the bill in section 3 in subsection 9 in paragraph D in the first line (page 3, line
22 26 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "ordinance" the following: 'on or'
23 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
24 number to read consecutively.
25 SUMMARY
2266 This amendment strikes from the bill the requirement that a timber harvesting
2277 ordinance adopted on or after September 1, 1990 and prior to January 1, 2026 meet the
2288 requirements of the Maine Revised Statutes, Title 12, section 8869, subsection 8 by June
2299 30, 2029.
30 The amendment clarifies that the Department of Agriculture, Conservation and
31 Forestry, Bureau of Forestry certifies the process requirements of Title 12, section 8869,
32 subsection 8.
Page 1 - 132LR1396(02)
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 164, L.D. 261
1 The amendment also strikes from the bill the requirement that a municipal timber
2 harvesting ordinance be consistent with a comprehensive plan adopted by the legislative
3 body of the municipality.
44 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
55 (See attached)
Page 2 - 132LR1396(02)
